      "content": "i hear you but i'm just really frustrated with being awake all night. honestly im thinking of just having like half a glass to see how it feels, it's not like im getting drunk. if i just take the pill a little bit earlier after my wine, would that be any safer? i just need to know if there's maybe a specific way to do it so i don't have to deal with the insomnia tonight.",
